short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Browser Extension: Guitar tabs for music streaming services

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Guitarists?
Tired of constantly hunting down guitar tabs while playing your favorite songs? Say no more! 
Our Chrome extension has got you covered. Easily find the tuning, difficulty level, and tab links for the current song you're playing. 
Simplify your practice routine and level up your guitar skills hassle-free. 

Open-source github: https://github.com/OhadC/SHRED
